title: Police Officer Bricked and Knocked Out
cleaned_text:
Police officer knocked out by brick to the head

 Fellow officer drag his body through crowd

A police officer was hit in the head by a brick shortly after an officer involved shooting of Jacob Blake in Kenosha last evening. The neighborhood upset with with the shooting and viral video retaliated and riots began. There are no updates on the condition of the officer, however Jacob Blake was moved from surgery to intensive care according to the MSM. Riots continued into the night leading to a car lot, church, garbage trucks, city buildings and more set ablaze.
